thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1i-%C3%8Dch-Quy/author-jxffn0kiYqR6Jxsac5acdA">Lại Ích Quy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/Nh%C4%A9-H%C3%A0-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-lWsXRPEpw6QJqX_SLn3LhQ">Nhĩ Hà kỳ 1 - 耳河其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ninh-T%E1%BB%91n/author-0zxx9ptNwfX9AYtkCUmYYQ">Ninh Tốn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Ung/S%C3%A1p-hoa-ng%C3%A2m/poem-kJ5i0ySuBZ2rxSiBCQoREg">Sáp hoa ngâm - 插花吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Ung/author-o_-PSNPz1uLA6fktF-flfQ">Thiệu Ung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Thu-v%C3%A3n-ho%C3%A0i-Mao-S%C6%A1n-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-H%C3%A0m-th%C3%B4n-x%C3%A1/poem-cnGgyxDvYheErPUweSUSxA">Thu vãn hoài Mao Sơn Thạch Hàm thôn xá - 秋晚懷茅山石涵村舍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ng%E1%BB%B1-h%C3%A0/poem-rZGPlyD7HZUYOrLB8Yjibg">Vịnh Ngự hà - 詠御河</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br></div>	</div>
